About me 

I am PhD candidate at Purdue University, stuyding under Prof. Krishna Jayant in the Nano Neurotechnology Lab. My research efforts focusses on understanding learning and decision making by developing novel technoolgies and protocols. 







"As followers of natural science we know nothing of any relation between thoughts and the brain, except as a gross correlation in time and space." ~ Charles Scott Sherrington

